title: John Densmore
itunes:title: John Densmore
description:
This week's episode of Questlove Supreme pairs Quest and Team Supreme with Rock and Roll royalty, hall of famer and legendary Doors drummer, John Densmore. Listen as John breaks down the creative process of Jim Morrison, life in one of the most rebellious bands of all time and shares his love for Stacey Abrams? You don't want to miss this one!
